Developer Terms of Use
des: We've clumped a pile of songs together and put them on shuffle. A variety of the best rock, pop, hip hop, dance and more! Whether you love classic rock, tend to crank up the pop music or prefer a little hip hop and modern rock music - Shuffle has created a playlist featuring a mishmash of songs that everyone will enjoy. The best part? You just never know what will play next. It's your songs - on shuffle.
